PrimePicks
PrimePicks is an e-commerce application designed to offer a seamless shopping experience. Developed using Spring Boot, this application integrates various Spring modules to deliver a robust, secure, and efficient platform. Below, you'll find details on the project's setup, architecture, and functionality.

Table of Contents
